        <h2>Event Details</h2>
        <p>Hacktoberfest Nashik is a month-long celebration of open source software held every October. It brings together developers, designers, and tech enthusiasts to contribute to open-source projects and enhance their skills while collaborating with like-minded individuals.</p>
        <p>This year, Hacktoberfest Nashik will feature workshops, talks, and networking opportunities to help participants gain valuable insights into the world of open source.</p>
